'''尼克·赫尔姆'''（{{lang-en|Nick Helm}}，1980/1981出生于[[聖奧爾本斯|聖奧爾本斯]]）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.scotsman.com/what-s-on/theatre-comedy-dance/interview-nick-helm-comedian-1-2462996|title=Interview, Nick Helm, comedian|publisher=The Scotsman|last=Richardson|first=Jay|date=11 August 2012|accessdate=2014-03-23|archive-date=2014-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222213543/http://www.scotsman.com/what-s-on/theatre-comedy-dance/interview-nick-helm-comedian-1-2462996|dead-url=no}}</ref>是一位英国[[喜劇演員|喜劇演員]]、[[演員|演員]]和[[音乐家|音乐家]]，由于作品的戏剧和对抗性而被知晓。<ref name=ta>{{cite news|last=Challis|first=Chris|title=Nick Helm: Dare To Dream|url=http://www.theargus.co.uk/theguide/stage/9097409.Nick_Helm__Dare_To_Dream__Upstairs_at_the_Three_and_Ten__Brighton__June_22/|accessdate=7 July 2011|newspaper=The Argus|date=22 June 2011}}</ref>他的风格常被形容为“傲慢和张扬的”。<ref name=ti>{{cite news|last=Hall|first=Julian|title=Nick Helm: Keep Hold of the Gold|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/comedy/reviews/nick-helm-keep-hold-of-the-gold-soho-theatre-london-2203769.html|accessdate=7 July 2011|newspaper=The Independent|date=4 February 2011|archive-date=2014-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140125125641/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/comedy/reviews/nick-helm-keep-hold-of-the-gold-soho-theatre-london-2203769.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2010年，他在爱丁堡边缘艺术节节目''Hold of the Gold''中表演后开始成名。2014年，赫尔姆于[[英國廣播公司第三台|英國廣播公司第三台]]情景喜剧《[[舅舅安迪|舅舅安迪]]》中担任主演。

2014年，他获得了[[南岸天空艺术奖|南岸天空艺术奖]]泰晤士突破奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sky.com/tv/show/south-bank-awards/article/winners-2014 |title=South Bank Sky Arts Winners 2014 |publisher=Sky.com |date= |accessdate=2014-01-28 |archive-date=2014-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140131095830/http://www.sky.com/tv/show/south-bank-awards/article/winners-2014 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
